        <p><strong>Category: Portable Multimedia Accessories</strong></p><p><strong>ZAGG Inc.</strong></p>
        <p><strong>ZAGGfolio</strong><br><a href="http://www.zagg.com" target="_blank">http://www.zagg.com</a></p>
        <p>Created with a stylish design and a durable microfiber lining, the ZAGGfolio is an impressively thin multi-function iPad folio case for Apple iPad 2, complete with a removable Bluetooth keyboard and a built-in stand system, ideal for on-the-go use.</p>
       
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<hr class="separator" /><div class="productListingLeft"><img src="/cesweb/media/CESWeb/Innovation%20Awards/2012%20Innovations%20Honorees/Portable%20Multimedia%20Accessories/ZAGGkeys.png" width="100" alt="ZAGGkeys FLEX" class="fancybox" href="/cesweb/media/CESWeb/Innovation%20Awards/2012%20Innovations%20Honorees/Portable%20Multimedia%20Accessories/ZAGGkeys_full.png"><br><a class="fancybox" href="/cesweb/media/CESWeb/Innovation%20Awards/2012%20Innovations%20Honorees/Portable%20Multimedia%20Accessories/ZAGGkeys_full.png" title="">Click to enlarge</a></div>
<div class="productListingRight">
    <div style="float: right; text-align: right;">
         
    </div>
        <p><strong>Category: Portable Multimedia Accessories</strong></p><p><strong>ZAGG Inc.</strong></p>
        <p><strong>ZAGGkeys FLEX</strong><br><a href="http://www.zagg.com" target="_blank">http://www.zagg.com</a></p>
        <p>Thin, lightweight, and compact, the ZAGGkeys FLEX is the most portable tablet keyboard of its kind. Wrapped in a polyurethane cover that converts into a stand, the FLEX is a universal keyboard for any bluetooth-enabled tablet or smartphone.</p>
       
</div>
